race.description: Ladbrokes Big Bets Copy Now Handicap (Bm78)
race.comment: TRUE AMOR (11) continued his outstanding form this prep when runner-up in a $250k Magic Millions race over 1300m at the Gold Coast three weeks ago. Has won three races and all have been at today's trip. Perfectly drawn so there is a lot to like about his chances. FLYING DESTINY (5) stalked the pace then battled on okay for a close fourth when resuming over this distance at Doomben last time out. Stepping up in class but his second-up record is strong and he maps beautifully from a good draw behind a hot tempo. SIR CARTER (1) made it two from two this prep when he led all the way and just held on in the $500k Magic Millions Country Cup recently. Speedy customer who will be in this for a long way. GOSPEL GIRL (8) is back from a 19-week spell. Has two wins and a placing from three previous tries at this track and trip. Good fresh performer who won a recent trial so looks ready to go.
